<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Nova Assinatura</h1>
  <%= link_to 'Voltar', subscriptions_path, class: "px-4 py-2 bg-gray-200 rounded-md text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-300" %>
</div>

<div class="bg-white overflow-hidden shadow rounded-lg">
  <div class="px-4 py-5 sm:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Dados da Assinatura</h2>
    
    <%= render 'form', subscription: @subscription %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-8 bg-white overflow-hidden shadow rounded-lg">
  <div class="px-4 py-5 sm:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Informações Importantes</h2>
    
    <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-3">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
            Após criar a assinatura, você poderá adicionar serviços adicionais específicos a ela.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4">
      <div class="flex">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-3">
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
            Lembre-se que todo pacote deve ter pelo menos um serviço adicional, conforme as regras de negócio.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
